Amendment No. 1 to Senate Bill 434
Amend Senate Bill 434 as originally introduced:
Page 1, delete lines 10 through 16, and substitute the following:
"CONCERNING THE PERCENTAGE OF VOTES REQUIRED FOR APPROVAL OF A CONSTITUTIONAL
AMENDMENT REFERRED TO VOTERS UNDER ARKANSAS CONSTITUTION, ARTICLE 5, § 1;
AMENDING ARKANSAS CONSTITUTION, ARTICLE 5, § 1, AS AUTHORIZED BY THAT
PROVISION OF THE ARKANSAS CONSTITUTION; TO DECLARE AN EMERGENCY; AND FOR
OTHER PURPOSES."
AND
Delete the subtitle in its entirety and substitute:
"TO CREATE THE "PROTECT OUR CONSTITUTION
ACT"; TO AMEND A PORTION OF THE ARKANSAS
CONSTITUTION AS AUTHORIZED BY ARKANSAS
CONSTITUTION, ARTICLE 5, § 1; AND TO
DECLARE AN EMERGENCY."
